io.gearpump.streaming.partitioner

Interface Partitioner

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MulticastPartitioner, UnicastPartitioner
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BroadcastPartitioner, CoLocationPartitioner, GroupByPartitioner, HashPartitioner, ShuffleGroupingPartitioner, ShufflePartitioner

    public interface Partitioner
extends scala.Serializable
    For processor chain: A (3 tasks) -> B (3 tasks), partitioner decide how ONE task of upstream processor A send to several tasks of downstream processor B.
